      "stem_html": "<img class=\"scaled-down\" src=\"https://exercises.openstax.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/proxy/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBcmNSIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--b3ec970fe3866616d84bcb668ae2b10f753a5ef1/OChem_07_06_009a.jpg\" alt=\"The first structure has a 4-carbon chain with double bond at C1. The second structure has a 3-carbon chain with double bond between C1-C2. C2 is bonded to methyl group.\">",
